# ğŸ“ Writing Tigrinya

**Writing Tigrinya** is a desktop application designed to help users write, edit, and format text in the **Tigrinya language** easily.  
The application aims to provide a **Tigrinya-centered alternative to Microsoft Word**, making digital writing more accessible for Tigrinya speakers.

Most popular word processors use English-based menus and tools, which can be challenging for users who primarily work in Tigrinya. This project focuses on simplifying the writing experience by putting the Tigrinya language first.

---

## ğŸ¯ Project Goals

- Enable easy and accurate writing of Tigrinya words  
- Provide basic text styling and formatting tools  
- Reduce dependency on English-language word processors  
- Support the growth of Tigrinya in digital environments  

---

## âœï¸ Features

- Simple and intuitive Tigrinya text input  
- Basic word styling and formatting  
- Lightweight and easy-to-use interface  
- Offline support for writing and editing  

---

## ğŸŒ Translation Feature

- Optional translation functionality  
- Translate from **Tigrinya to other languages**  
- Translate from **other languages to Tigrinya**  
- Requires an active internet connection  

---

## ğŸ§© Target Users

- Native Tigrinya speakers  
- Students, teachers, and writers  
- Users who find English-based word processors difficult  
- Anyone interested in promoting the Tigrinya language digitally  

---

